  "detailed_description": "<h1>Join the Discord</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><strong>Ashes of the Union</strong> — a vehicular shooter with roguelike elements, offering a wild take on an alternate future of the Soviet Union. Build your combat vehicle and show nature who's boss!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3091390/extras/0e92f8eab182ac331a681047367e5f1e.poster.avif?t=1731512207\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3091390/extras/0e92f8eab182ac331a681047367e5f1e.webm?t=1731512207\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3091390/extras/0e92f8eab182ac331a681047367e5f1e.mp4?t=1731512207\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Soviet Post-Apocalypse:</strong> Immerse yourself in an atmosphere where your cozy communal apartment has been replaced by an autonomous bunker. Forget about cats and dogs. In this world, your favorite \"pets\" will be giant Hornbeetles and deadly Chewercrabs. But don't worry, they don't bite... too painfully.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3091390/extras/c705e0b44baf5bbb4fd061cf7dc77b96.poster.avif?t=1731512207\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3091390/extras/c705e0b44baf5bbb4fd061cf7dc77b96.webm?t=1731512207\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3091390/extras/c705e0b44baf5bbb4fd061cf7dc77b96.mp4?t=1731512207\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Equipping your vehicle with various weapons:</strong> Soviet-style tuning! Turn your old \"Bukhanka\" into a fortress on wheels with rocket launchers and laser cannons. Now you're not just driving through the wastelands, you're taming them!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3091390/extras/9258217f605624a65f38b8ab4ad5bf20.poster.avif?t=1731512207\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3091390/extras/9258217f605624a65f38b8ab4ad5bf20.webm?t=1731512207\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3091390/extras/9258217f605624a65f38b8ab4ad5bf20.mp4?t=1731512207\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Exploring the map and searching for resources:</strong> Trips through the ruins have never been so exciting! Ride through the wreckage, collect rare resources, and avoid poisonous mists because we don't have an antidote (yet).<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3091390/extras/6e4bb5010805e92f7eb768c70f547b75.poster.avif?t=1731512207\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3091390/extras/6e4bb5010805e92f7eb768c70f547b75.webm?t=1731512207\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3091390/extras/6e4bb5010805e92f7eb768c70f547b75.mp4?t=1731512207\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Models of Soviet technology: </strong>Feel the power and reliability of Soviet engineering! Use a variety of vehicles, from \"GAZ\" to \"Ural,\" to traverse dangerous territories and fight monsters.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3091390/extras/7c31b177b82acd72a1e3e7dbc49bb2ac.poster.avif?t=1731512207\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3091390/extras/7c31b177b82acd72a1e3e7dbc49bb2ac.webm?t=1731512207\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3091390/extras/7c31b177b82acd72a1e3e7dbc49bb2ac.mp4?t=1731512207\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Technological development:</strong> From the Kalashnikov tank machine gun to the laser cannon, from ordinary wooden planks to the strongest cast armor. Upgrade your technology to increase your chances of survival and become the king (or queen) of the wastelands.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3091390/extras/74f822a3491626ec61870ec3ee62f0a3.poster.avif?t=1731512207\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3091390/extras/74f822a3491626ec61870ec3ee62f0a3.webm?t=1731512207\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3091390/extras/74f822a3491626ec61870ec3ee62f0a3.mp4?t=1731512207\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Are you ready for new adventures in a world where only ingenuity and the good old \"PKT\" will help you survive? Let's roll, comrade!<br><br>",
